# lint-github-workflow

Linter for GitHub Workflow definitions.

Install the `ghwflint` CLI utility and Python package with;

```bash
pip install ghwflint
```

## Usage

Lint a GitHub Workflow definition with:

```bash
ghwflint -- .github/workflows/build.yml
```

## Development

### Build

Build with Poetry:

```shell
poetry install
```

Run locally with your favorite shell:

```bash
./bin/ghwflint --help
```

Alternatively, install as a Python module:

```shell
poetry build
pip install --force-reinstall dist/*.whl
ghwflint --help
```

Be aware that when making changes to the CLI, you would need to re-install the module.

### Release

Publish to PyPI with Poetry & Twine:

```shell
poetry version patch
poetry build
twine upload dist/*.whl
```

